<p><span id="u-credit-00513" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00513" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00513-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4142571&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180081" alt="Dr Hormress" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4142571)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;">Dr Hormress</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1609587134 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">02 Jan 2021 11:32</span></p>
</div>
